mujhe jeene do ( english : let me live ) is a 1963 hindi film directed by moni bhattacharya . the film stars sunil dutt , waheeda rehman , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy , nirupa roy and nirupa roy . the film was remade in hindi as mujhe jeene ka &lt;unk&gt; .